《'''血染好萊塢'''》（{{lang-en|''Hollywood's Bleeding''}}）是美國歌手[[波兹·马龙|波兹·马龙]]的第三張錄音室專輯。專輯由[[聯眾唱片|聯眾唱片]]於2019年9月6日發行。專輯找來{{tsl|en|Andrew Watt (musician)|安德魯·瓦特}}、[[BloodPop|BloodPop]]、{{tsl|en|Brian Lee (songwriter)||布莱恩·李}}、Carter Lang、{{le|DJ Dahi}}、{{le|埃米爾·海尼|Emile Haynie}}、[[弗蘭克·杜克斯|弗蘭克·杜克斯]]、Happy Perez、Jahaan Sweet、[[路易斯·貝爾|路易斯·貝爾]]、Matt Tavares、{{le|尼克·米拉|Nick Mira}}、Wallis Lane和馬龍本人等人製作，是張帶有[[嘻哈音樂|嘻哈]]與[[流行_(音樂類型)|流行]]風格的專輯<ref name="Pitchfork">{{cite web |url=https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/post-malone-hollywoods-bleeding/ |title=Post Malone: Hollywood's Bleeding Album Review |website=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork]] |last=Greene |first=Jason |date=2019-09-10 |accessdate=2019-09-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190910235513/https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/post-malone-hollywoods-bleeding/ |archivedate=2019-09-10 |language=en |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="Consequence of Sound">{{cite web |url=https://consequenceofsound.net/2019/09/album-review-post-malone-hollywoods-bleeding/ |title=Post Malone – Hollywood's Bleeding |website=[[Consequence_of_Sound|Consequence of Sound]] |last=Weiss |first=Dan |date=2019-09-11 |accessdate=2019-09-11 |language=en |deadurl=no |archive-date=2019-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211185053/https://consequenceofsound.net/2019/09/album-review-post-malone-hollywoods-bleeding/ }}</ref>。

